text: Escape to the serene woods of Point Roberts to this well-maintained home featuring 2 beds and 2 baths. This home offers all-season living and a bright open-concept layout with large windows and vaulted ceilings. Expansive kitchen and dining area that overlook the gardens with sliding doors onto the deck. Private setting with views from every window of beautiful evergreen trees. Don't miss out on this charming home!

Freshly updated & ready for new owners. You'll fall in love with this charming single level home right in the heart of Bellingham! Within walking distance to parks, trails, schools, Trader Joes, Sunnyland, & so much more. Recently renovated including all new LVP flooring throughout, brand new kitchen & bathrooms with soft close cabinets & quartz countertops, subway tiled backsplash, dining area, & all appliances included. 3 nice sized bedrooms. Cozy living room with tons of natural light, a gas fireplace, plus a separate family room that could easily be a 4th bedroom, office, TV room, which has a slider out to the back deck. The new cedar fence gives the backyard great privacy. Large storage shed & an attached 2 car carport. Move-in ready!

Great building lot - Private and sunny south facing. It has been partially cleared and improved with two culverts, horseshoe driveway and leveled building site. Also has an approved septic design and a brand new heavy duty metal shed installed with concrete floor. Walk to Monument Park with Beach Access.

The possibilities are endless w/ this unique north Bellingham location! Room to spread out w/ just over 4 acres of property holding 2 homes, 2 shops, 3 storage buildings & large barn. Perhaps a hobby farm w/ it's idyllic setting, yet quick access to I-5 & Ferndale. Your main home is tucked back off the road & features 3 beds, 2 baths. Sit in the sun on your front porch or on the shaded/covered back deck. The smaller home in front w/ 2 beds, 1 bath, new interior paint & flooring. Each home is on their own septic. Shop one is 48x30, 3 bays plus an RV door. Shop two houses two offices, 3/4 bath, plus wood shop & storage loft. Other features: storage sheds, carports/lean-tos, fruit trees, goat pens, chicken coop, small pond, fire pit and more.

Fully fenced and gated single level 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home. Home features large covered front porch, covered back deck, brick and cement board siding, Kitchen has plenty of cabinets, stainless appliances, granite counters. Large primary bedroom with walk in closet and en-suite bathroom double sinks. Open floor plan with plenty of natural light. Landscaping includes Cherry, Plum, and Asian Pear trees. Large paved circular driveway for convenient access in and out. Security windows and door package. Large garden shed is included.

Welcome to Crossridge Urban Community! Brand new single family homes that have been thoughtfully designed with architectural & community integrity, each home feels custom with its elevated finishes and interior design. The Heliotrope model has all the living on the main floor including primary bedroom with en suite. Indoor/outdoor living onto a large covered patio to your private backyard with 6' fence, gate, modern pavers, solar lighting, low maint turf and raised bed planters. Upstairs you'll find 2 more bedrooms with an additional full bath. Don't forget the detached flex space with half bath accessed through garage that can be used as an office, family room, or for guests.

If a thoroughly contemporary experience with outstanding access to trails and all the eateries and conveniences offered by Fairhaven are important, there really isnt a good reason to look further than this 2016 built 3 bed 2 bath masterpiece. This home is 1, 972 square feet of contemporary luxury with a glass roll up door flooding the living space with light and fresh air. Zoned radiant floors warm the space and visitors will marvel at the reclaimed timber accents and open kitchen. Built for entertaining, this home blurs the concept of indoor and outdoor spaces and has room for additional dwellings per the new state code. After the guest depart, the entire upstairs is a primary suite, complete with private deck and steam sauna/shower!

Positioned high above the 6th hole of beautiful Birch Bay Village's private golf course w/HUGE panoramic views of Mt. Baker, Course Ponds, San Juans, the Bay & more from almost every room. Private Lane brings you to this Frank Lloyd Wright inspired custom. Still in it's original T&G Cedar design, this home begs for a modern makeover into a contemporary masterpiece or proudly enjoy as it is. Sunrises are epic & stay cozy around the retro gas fireplace in the huge vaulted great room after sunset. Huge garage+ dbl carport. The Village is a gated community w/24/7 manned security, newly constructed 250 slip marina, Golf course, Clubhouse, Pool, Pickleball, tennis, beach parks & more. Come Home to a Vacation, Come Home to Birch Bay Village.

Top corner OCEANFRONT condo at the highly desirable Sands Condominiums in Birch Bay! Easy open floorplan with laminate flooring includes comfy den PLUS oceanfront living room with cozy gas fireplace. Your private deck includes a storage closet & has room for dining or lounge chairs for relaxing, enjoying the sunset & just taking it all in! Kitchen includes all stainless appliances plus more beach views from the side window. Spacious primary bedroom also boasts a STUNNING view, double closets & an ensuite bathroom. Guest bedroom & bathroom, plus in-unit washer & dryer complete everything you need for a getaway vacation spot or full-time living. Enjoy the walking trail, crabbing, clamming, boating and all the best Birch Bay has to offer!

Charming rambler in sought after Ridgemont neighborhood, just steps from Ridgemont Park that features a playground, basketball court, and large grassy area. Excellent schools. Features an adorable backyard shed, tons of privacy, and a fully fenced yard. Recent updates include a new roof, new skylight & new hot water heaters. Primary bedroom features walk-in closet and french doors to light-filled en-suite bathroom with deep jetted soaker tub. Enjoy garden space, hardwood floors, a rec room with a wood-burning fireplace, and a deck perfect for backyard BBQs. Updates throughout. The cherry on top is the optimal location! Close to I-5, WWU, Sehome high school, grocery stores, downtown and Lake Padden/Galbraith. Offers due 7pm 6/17

Start living your PNW dream in this beautifully designed and maintained Gate 1 home! Your open concept, main level living space includes your primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet, cozy gas fireplace in the living room, and a light & bright dining space that opens up to your fabulous deck. Enjoy cooking in your charming kitchen with stainless steel appliances, & plenty of counter and cabinet space for storage. Two additional bedrooms, ample parking/outdoor space, plus a fully finished basement make this home perfect for hosting & entertaining. Nows your chance to live the lakeside lifestyle & experience all Sudden Valleys amenities including the professional 18-hole golf course, nearby beaches, marina, trails, & more!

First time on the market, welcome to this private estate property, offering a unique blend of country living in the city. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the charm of 70's architecture & flooded with natural light. Main level living offering an expansive deck with partial views of Bellingham Bay & the San Juan Islands. Open concept kitchen/dining complete with 4 bedrooms & 2nd kitchen & living room downstairs, this home offers unique living spaces. Outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the access to trails & exploring the natural beauty surrounding the property. The detached shop provides ample space for hobbies, storage, or even a workshop. Embrace the tranquility & space to make this one of a kind property your own.

Excellent location in the wonderful town of Lynden, situated on a salmon spawning creek feeding the Nooksack River. This desirable 3-bedroom 2-bath daylight rambler has lower-level secondary bonus/family room w/ perfect MIL possibilities + 2 large storage areas/rooms. Large back deck overlooking the creek creates a covered area off the 2nd living space on those rainy days. Positioned in a peaceful cul-de-sac of an established neighborhood & just a few blocks to downtown to Lyndens quaint restaurants & stores.

Welcome to this fully fenced garden oasis nestled in Cordata's Springs, Built Green solar community. This home offers breathtaking territorial views of Mt. Baker from its sunny southwest-facing position. Home features 3bedrm, 3bathrms, and a spacious 2-car garage at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. Equipped with 10 solar panels and a mini-split system for heating and cooling, home ensures energy efficiency. Ethernet wiring supports a robust home network, and the garage is prepped for electric vehicles. Enjoy upgraded kitchen appliances, expansive community open spaces, and neighborhood parks. The HOA takes care of the front yard lawn and shrubs. Easy access to major retailers and amenities.

Extraordinary 3 bed, 2.75 bath custom-built home nestled on a sunlit cul-de-sac lot, boasting breathtaking mountain views. This home is designed for seamless entertaining, featuring an expansive open floor plan, vaulted wood ceiling, open stairway, & a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The main floor offers a luxurious primary suite. Step outside to discover an oversized deck & a secluded hot tub, perfect for relaxation & gatherings. This property presents a rare opportunity to own a stunning Glacier retreat, with the potential of a separate ground-floor unit ideal for hosting or generating rental income. Residents enjoy access to a clubhouse, tennis courts, pool, sauna, & more. Experience the epitome of mountain living in this remarkable home.

Escape to luxury and tranquility in this exquisite Geneva home, boasting privacy and proximity to Bellingham's best. The main floor features a lavish primary bedroom with spa-like en-suite bath, adorned with ceramic tile flooring, granite double-vanity, & rejuvenating soaker tub. Entertain effortlessly in the gourmet kitchen w/center island & pantry for culinary delights. Upstairs, two spacious bedrooms & above garage bonus room offers space versatility. The 14, 810 sf lot provides ample space for outdoor relaxation & hobbies. Rear trex deck is ideal for sunny days. New carpet throughout enhances comfort, while a new high-efficiency furnace. Experience the epitome of refined living, schedule your tour today! Home is virtually staged.

Build equity in this stick built home in Birch Bay. Bring your skills and visions to renovate this home and make it yours or potential rental investment. Partial views of Birch Bay and Mt. Baker. 2 bedrooms 1 & 1/2 baths. Possible 3rd bedroom. 3 out buildings. Fenced back yard. 15 minutes from the Peace Arch border crossing into Canada.

Welcome to The Glen! This very thoughtful floorplan will be your base for a lifetime of adventures and memories in the Foothills of Mt Baker! Many recent projects completed which means the maintenance is on cruise control. Newer plumbing, metal roofs, furnace, water heater - just come enjoy! This fun and inviting community hosts events year-round making socializing easy. Boasting 2 pools, disc-golf, river access, horseshoes, playgrounds, trails, sauna, tennis courts, library and 24/7 security make this a safe retreat for all ages! Queen size bed in main Bd, 2 - built-in Full size beds, each in their own sleeping quarters + an added enclosed porch means up to 5 private sleeping areas. Recreationally zoned, restricted to 120 days of use/year.

This beautiful single-level Edgemoor estate is truly one of a kind. The well-designed floor plan makes it an entertainer's dream, with seamless indoor-outdoor flow and ample square footage for hosting guests. Stunning bay and island views can be enjoyed from nearly every room, showcasing the beauty of the neighborhood and its surroundings. The chef's kitchen, equipped with updated stainless appliances, opens up to a heated covered patio featuring a gas fireplace and an outdoor BBQ kitchenette. The expansive yard and mature landscaping create a tranquil and private enclave in this sought-after neighborhood. This home presents a unique opportunity in Bellingham's south side, offering a perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and natural beauty.

Bright, clean, well kept 2bd/ 1bath in Lakeway Estates 55+ Community. This home features a sunny kitchen with bay windows, recently upgraded bathroom with extra large walk-in shower, spacious covered deck, and extra large carport. As part of the 55+ park, residents have access to the updated community center with kitchen, library, pool tables, as well as a variety of community events. Excellent location close to shopping, restaurants, services, public transportation, and easy I-5 access. Seller will include personal items in the home, which include a newer adjustable bed, power lift recliner, sofa, tables, and washer/dryer.

Live the vacation lifestyle year-round in this beautifully finished, 2 bed, 1.75 bath condo! Featuring vaulted ceilings for an airy feel, 6 walls for extra privacy & a lovely view overlooking the Sudden Valley Golf Course, this space is the ideal part-time or full-time abode. Your gorgeous kitchen offers vinyl plank floors, custom cabinets, timeless stainless-steel appliances, & granite countertops for added luxury. Enjoy the walk-in closet & fairway views from your spacious primary bedroom & the fabulous marble-topped double sink + tiled walk-in shower in the primary bath. Your huge living room with cozy, wood-burning fireplace & slider to your view deck + access to all Sudden Valley amenities make this one a showstopper!

A stunning home, known as the Jewel of the Neighborhood. Fully updated & customized, yet retains the charm of its era. Main bath w/soaker tub. Primary bedroom/bath w/walk in shower. Siberian Birch wood floors, raised panel solid hemlock doors & craftsman trim throughout. Gourmet kitchen w/large granite island & countertops, custom maple cabinets, quality stainless appliances. Laundry room, W/D included. Cozy gas F/P, Full attic access w/ample storage. Unfinished basement for unlimited use: wine cellar/shop/storage. Oversized 1.5 car garage. A split-level deck leading to a gorgeous 800 sf paver courtyard where trees, fences, flowers and block walls create privacy for entertaining.This beautiful, beloved home will welcome you with open arms!

The gorgeous acreage you've been waiting for is here! Located on a flat, cleared, shy-5-acre parcel, this beautifully updated 3-bed/2-bath home combines modern appeal with rural charm into one unique experience. Tree-lined driveway leads you to a cute single-level home with open layout, sunny kitchen with island + stainless steel appliances, and spacious primary suite with 3/4 bath and sauna! Recent updates include roof, deck, interior + exterior paint, carpet, concrete foundation skirting, and power to the 36' x 36' barn with loft and 3 stalls. Featuring garden space, fruit trees, and equestrian possibilities, there's something for everyone. Your piece of paradise awaits!

Wonderful sought after one-level condo in this popular 55+ community. This spacious 3 bedroom 2 bath 1700 sq ft home has a great location at the end of the lane. Kitchen cabinets, countertops, appliances have been updated and there's a cozy fireplace in the vaulted-ceiling living/dining room. Outside is beautifully landscaped with handy access to the clubhouse featuring a indoor pool/hot tub, exercise room, and gathering space. Plus RV storage available. Conveniently located near new city park, shopping, medical facilities, and easy freeway access. Come take a look.

Private just shy of 5 acres near Galbraith Mountain is highly sought after and provides easy access to nature trails and recreational activities. Close to I-5, Lake Padden and all amenities. Currently no access, marketable timber is included.

Nestled along the scenic fairways of the golf course, this spacious 3700+ sq ft custom-built one owner home is now available for the first time. This generous 3-bedroom home hosts 2 ensuites, with additional living space and office upstairs. Enjoy the architectural marvels like vaulted ceilings and large windows that flood the home with natural light, serene views and wildlife. With its thoughtfully designed layout, this home provides the perfect canvas for your personal touches. Enjoy comfort and style in the vibrant community offering amenities - private beaches, seasonal pool, parks, gym, marina, & the 18-hole championship golf course.

New Modern Construction home in Lynden. This Luxury home has 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, 2 living rooms, office, 2 primary bedrooms w/ attached elegant bathrooms, walk in tiled showers & walk in closets, the primary bedroom upstairs has a private deck with mountain view. Elegant Kitchen with lots of cabinets, stainless steel appliances, soft close cabinets, Quartz, Spice kitchen with oven, sink, Dishwasher, cabinets. Large Dining area with lower covered deck so you can access your large back yard. stone wrapped gas fireplace in the lower living room, upstairs living room with deck out back that spans the length of the back of the house. House has Solar installed, EV Charger installed, on one of the largest lots. close to Vancouver. Finished

Desirable ground floor WATER VIEW condo in Jacobs Landing! This 880sf 2 BD 1 BA unit works perfectly for a full-time residence, beach getaway, or short/long-term AirBB/VRBO rental. Completely remodeled recently with all NEW kitchen cabinets, appliances, flooring, bathroom tile, fireplace, doors, light fixtures, & more! Take in the fabulous ocean view & sunsets from your living room or walk out onto your garden patio with beautifully landscaped grassy area & just steps directly to the beach. Enjoy Jacobs Landing amenities including an indoor pool, hot tub, private clubhouse, tennis & racquetball courts. PLUS boating, crabbing, clamming, walking the berm & nearby restaurants. Centrally located in Birch Bay, minutes to 1-5 and US/CAN border.

One of 20 new homes by Skeers Construction in Hannah Creek. This is the ultimate PNW lifestyle location with access to 65+ miles of world class mountain biking, hiking, and trail running on the adjacent 3000 acre Galbraith Mountain trail system. Whatcom Falls Park is just down the street, and downtown is less than 3 miles away. This 4 bedroom plan features dramatic vaulted ceilings in the entry foyer, a main floor home office, and a covered patio for year round outdoor enjoyment. High tech energy features include innovative AeroBarrier building envelope air sealing, heat pump heating and cooling with energy recovery ventilation (ERV) system, and a super efficient hybrid heat pump hot water heater. Scheduled for July 2024 completion.

Dazzling, unique, gem of a home! Lovingly cared for w/ plenty of light through many large windows. Immaculate inside & beautifully landscaped outside, sitting on a quiet, treelined non-thru street! Enjoy morning sun inside living room or on the stunning outdoor patio! Quality wood shelving & cabinets stay. Newly updated kitchen w/ cherry cabinets, granite countertops & pass thru to dining room. Plenty of room for entertaining! Loads of closets! Each room views an amazing variety of mature trees. Master has step-in shower! Cute gazebo in cultivated grassless yard. Large 2 car garage w/ workspace & oodles of cabinets/shelving. Nearby beautiful Whatcom Falls Park trails, only minutes to Bellingham shops, restaurants, WWU & local hospital.

Looking for privacy / serenity? Come take a look at this vacant lot located below the road, and in an amazing setting - with green-belt behind. The adjacent vacant lot to the right is owned by Sudden Valley and has been turned into permanent green-belt. The property is down-sloping, making it conducive for a home plan with main level living and a day-light basement. The slope in the building area is gentle, so you could also work with a normal 2-story home plan (going up). Enjoy a very peaceful neighborhood with territorial views over the green-belt and neighborhood. The neighboring property at 25 Rose Ridge Loop looks like it is in the permit process for a new home - which will enhance the neighborhood greatly.

The Lupine by MainVue Homes at Horizon is an expensive design you dont want to miss. The Outdoor Room is located at the front of the home, providing an all-season escape to enjoy sweeping mountain and ocean views. The Kitchen is flush with 3m Quartz counters, Stainless Steel appliances, designer lighting and a Grand Butlers Pantry w/garage access. Enjoy the open-flow layout between the Great Room, Gourmet Kitchen, and Dining Room & Multi-Purpose Room at the rear of the home. Upstairs, find the Grand Suite w/free-standing tub & walk-in shower, followed by the Leisure Room & three secondary bedrooms. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission or commission is reduced.

Brand new highly upgraded home located adjacent to one of Sudden Valley's largest waterfront parks - Morning & Afternoon Beach. Enter the massive living / great room & enjoy 12 foot ceiling, luxury plank flooring, gas fireplace, and a large covered deck at the rear of the home overlooking Morning Beach Park. The platted trail down to the lakeside park is adjacent to this home. Kitchen offers high-end stainless appliances (gas cooktop), walk-in pantry, and 8' island with quartz countertop. Downstairs features Primary suite w/large ensuite walk-in closet & amazing full bath with large tiled shower, 2 guest bedrooms, den / family room, & a massive recreation room w/full wet bar & bar refrigerator. 2nd deck below with access to the trail.

10 acre lot adjacent to Galbraith Mountain trails yet close to schools, shopping, I-5 Lake Padden and Lake Whatcom. Marketable timber is included. Currently no access. Current zoning is 6 units per one acre, buyer to confirm. Great parcel for recreation or come build your dream home!

Escape to your own slice of Pacific Northwest paradise with this 3-bedroom rambler nestled on just shy of 8 acres of pristine wilderness. Situated in a private enclave, this home offers unparalleled tranquility and seclusion, yet is conveniently located just 35 minutes from Bellingham. With close proximity to the mountains, trails, and lakes, outdoor enthusiasts will delight in endless recreational opportunities year-round, from hiking and biking to fishing and boating and skiing. This house is ready for you to make it your home.

This turn-key, lovingly maintained property backs up to a breathtaking view of the Nooksack river and surrounding mountains. Outside boasts a large cover deck and upgrades such as a new 1000 gal septic tank, updated gazebo, patio rails, wood storage, workshop, fenced side yard, and landscape lighting. Inside the bright and airy park model, youll find new stainless steel appliances, new furniture including a sleeper sofa, TV, chairs and tables, and a hot water heater added 2021. The Glen is zoned recreational for 120 days of use out of the year and has all the amenities you could want, including 2 pools, hot tub, tennis court, library, laundry mat, 2 clubhouses, 24 hr security, gated entry, & play areas.

Feel like you're living on vacation year-round in this well-maintained home, located in the beautiful community of Birch Bay Village. As you enter into the main living areas of the house, you will notice the vaulted ceilings with skylights and windows on every wall, allowing for natural light to fill the space. Brand new carpet throughout, this home feels fresh and clean. Primary bedroom overlooks the serene back yard, complete with an ensuite bathroom. The star of the show has to be the outdoor living area with a large covered deck, paved patio, studio, and garden with fruit trees - all backing up to a private field. It really is an outdoor oasis! Community features golf course, private beaches, pool, marina, sport courts & more!

Penthouse Condo w/ expansive, 180-degree views of Bellingham Bay, the City, Orcas Island & the Cascade Mountains! This 2 bed, 1.75 bath has an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings & numerous windows capture an abundance of natural light. Custom cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances in kitchen & dining area. Sliding doors lead to a private balcony that captures the view of the Bay. Quality bamboo flooring, slate & ceramic throughout. Unit has Tankless H2O Heater, radiant heat throughout, and plenty of storage under stairs. Private entrance, spacious private patio & located adjacent to green space! Walkable location to parks, trails, schools & Downtown Bellingham! Unique opportunity for primary residence or potential rental.

Classic redone Farmhouse on 4.85 acres. Three bedrooms, walk-in pantry, light and bright country kitchen, and an adjacent sunroom. The property features, pastureland, woods, great sun exposure, garden area, barn, outbuildings, fully fenced acres, an animal turnout area, a stream cutting through the back of property, chicken coop and so much more. If you are looking for a country lifestyle, this is the one! 10 minutes from downtown Ferndale and Bellingham.

Stunning west facing views of Vancouver Island, Semiahmoo Bay and the Strait of Georgia from this ultra luxury waterfront penthouse. Enjoy high ceilings, an intelligent open design, chef's kitchen with high end appliances, and a spa inspired bath in the primary suite. Floor to ceiling windows encompass the living room & primary bedroom. Immerse yourself in outdoor living year-round with a large, covered deck that is perfect for dining al fresco while enjoying spectacular sunsets, and all the activity the ocean has to offer. Embrace an active lifestyle adjacent to the renown Semiahmoo Resort with 5-star dining, biking, hiking, golfing, and a large marina with available slips. Don't miss this rare opportunity!

Affordable opportunity to own a doublewide with an attached garage. The garage is extra deep which provides extra storage or makes a great workspace. Fenced back yard and garden shed too! Built in ramp into home for easy access. Open concept living area with vaulted ceilings. 2 bedrooms and 1 1/2 baths plus an office space. electric mini split for heat and AC Quiet community close to parks, library, shopping and restaurants.

A masterpiece of design & construction. Nestled on a shy 5 acres, this Timberframe home boasts soaring ceilings & walls of windows that frame stunning views of Baker from nearly every room. Designed for culinary excellence, chef's kitchen fts a prep sink, granite counters & top-of-the-line Lacanche range. Main level living; primary BR fts luxurious en-suite w/clawfoot tub, bespoke tilework & abundance of natural light. Upstairs will greet you w/a lofted office/flex space, 2 BRs & updated bath. Brimming w/updates: newer roof, newer exterior paint, new interior paint, refinished hardwood floors, new carpet. Large shop/barn w/finished upstairs studio. Tranquil pond & manicured grounds create idyllic backdrop for hobby farm or horse enthusiasts

A rare opportunity to own a 3-bedroom home at an AMAZING price! This well-loved home boasts vaulted ceilings, open concept, bathroom and walk in closet of primary and ample natural light. Back patio entrance is off of the laundry room with a semi private back yard. Hidden Village RV park has a heated pool, community center, playground and beautiful pond. No age restriction community.

Beautifully well built 3 bed home with modern updates and style in the Village at King Mountain! Newer LVP flooring throughout the main floor, top of the line kitchen features granite counters, white shaker cabinetry, an island w/ ample storage and an incredible pantry + wine closet. Open concept main level with white stone wrapped gas fireplace and beautiful large & bright windows + easy access to the fenced back yard. Spa like vaulted primary bed & bath with double sinks, walk-in shower, and custom walk-in closet. High quality carpet upstairs, full guest bath, conveniently located laundry room, and nook perfect for your Peloton, desk, or reading nook. Tucked back in the cul-de-sac with easy park and trail access. Large garage w/ storage.

Welcome to your dream home! Built in 2022, this 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom beauty is situated on a bright and sunny lot, offering an abundance of natural light creating an open and airy feel. Main floor primary bedroom features a 5 piece bathroom and huge walk-in closet. The expansive family room upstairs provides the perfect space for entertaining, relaxing, working or creating a home theater. The spa-like bathrooms are designed for ultimate comfort and relaxation, and each bedroom is equipped with its own ductless mini-split system for personalized climate control. The home features durable vinyl plank flooring, sleek quartz countertops, ample storage and a cozy gas fireplace. Step outside to a low maintenance yard and lovely, covered patio.

Come and see this updated unit in a beautiful 55+ community. It has been almost 2 years since the last 1 bedroom condo at the very desirable and private gated community of El Dorado went for sale. The unit has had major upgrades over the last few years including: in 2021 new kitchen appliances, the interior was painted, and new vinyl plank flooring was installed. In April of 2023 the seller purchased a new washer and dryer. For any storage needs, there is also a detached 1 car garage with remote control entry. This private community has a large clubhouse, 2 fully furnished guest rental units for the owners guests, a dog run, and a shared garden. Close to all the amenities you could possibly need, this unit is ready to go.

Welcome to your dream home nestled between Bellingham & Ferndale with it's many amenities. This charming, single level residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience & functionality. This 3 bd 1.5 bath 1421sq ft. home includes a spacious layout, inviting living room with a gas fireplace and huge picture window creating a warm, cozy atmosphere. Enjoy the large kitchen with tons of storage and counterspace. Step out to the lovely backyard and patio offering endless possibilities with a new garden shed for additional storage for your tools and outdoor equipment. Freshly painted exterior and newly hydroseeded lawn. The large 2 car garage, high efficiency furnace and AC make this home even better. Don't miss out on this gem of a home.

Seize the chance to create your ideal retreat on Lummi Island, where this vacant lot awaits the realization of your dream home or cabin. The property is ready for construction, featuring a potential building site and the convenience of readily available utilities, including a two-bedroom septic system already in place. Enjoy the amenities Scenic Estates & Lummi Island have to offer, including access to a refreshing swimming lake, a saltwater boat launch, a private beach, and a clubhouse. Furthermore, revel in the serene backdrop as the lot abuts hundreds of acres of forested land.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: Welcome to Bay Crest, one of Birch Bay's most desirable neighborhoods, where beach-town living is at its finest! This spacious 2, 138 sqft home features 4 bedrooms, an upstairs recreation room, and a roomy 3-car garage. Enjoy easy access to the beach via a short trail just across the street, and relax in the fully fenced backyard complete with a fire pit and patio, ideal for summer gatherings. Meticulously maintained and pre-inspected, this home also boasts updated appliances and flooring. The upstairs laundry room provides convenience for all bedrooms, while the primary suite offers privacy, a large walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom. Move in and enjoy a delightful summer in this exceptional home!

Welcome to the premier Lake Whatcom condo you've been waiting for! With lake views from every room this single-level, 2 bedroom condo is steps to your dreams. Walking distance to the quiet & calm AM PM beach with kayak storage, marina with boat storage, golf course & all amenities offered in Sudden Valley including the pool, fitness center & clubhouse. Recently completely remodeled with new floors, countertops, cabinets, paint and top-of-the-line appliances. High-end trim package & doors. New bay window recently installed to take in the stunning lake views. Primary bedroom with private deck also with lake views! Building has been freshly resided & roof installed. Carport directly in front for easy parking. Live vacation life full-time!

Come home to this beautiful waterfront single-level in Birch Bay Village! Enjoy your 75 feet of Thunderbird Lake frontage and views from your deck and most rooms in the home. New paint inside and out! The interior of the home is bathed in natural light with huge windows and skylights. Large great room/kitchen open up to tremendous views and right out to the deck. Sun room has massive windows and views; use as an office, yoga/art studio, library, etc. Enjoy the large primary suite and its gas fireplace/stove. Bring your boat and golf clubs! Birch Bay Village has 24/7 gated security w/ guard, pickleball & tennis courts, clubhouse, dog park, private Golf course, 250 slip marina, and community beachfront parks.

Idyllic location between the warms sands of Maple Beach and the forested walking trails of Lily Point. This level building lot is located on Madrona Place, a dead-end street in a very quiet neighborhood. A culvert, long driveway and clearing are complete and await your future dream home. Come enjoy the peace and tranquility of Point Roberts!

Opportunity knocks hard on the door of this 4-bedroom rambler right on the trails. Tucked in a low-traffic residential neighborhood walking distance to school, groceries and margaritas-- this stairless wonder is a rare chance to establish permanence and build wealth with some primer and creativity. Property offers two separate living spaces: main unit has 3 bedrooms 1 full bath; auxiliary studio has full bath and separate entrance. Fenced, sunny backyard is private with deck off living. Relax and take in the sounds of the birdlife and the bubbling of Fever Creek (which hasnt flooded, even in 2021). Large fully-applianced eat-in kitchen, newer gas furnace & H2o, plus plenty of off-street parkingall right in the middle of everything.

Beautifully maintained 1296 sq. ft. 2 bedroom/2 bath manufactured home in the ALL AGES park of Ferndale Mobile Estates. This home is completely move in ready with an oversized kitchen open to the large, light filled living room. Enjoy the generous sized master bathroom with built-ins. Many money saving features including a young furnace, new/young stainless steel appliances, young double paned windows, and young roof! Porches and steps also recently rebuilt. This home has two driveways which can accomodate up to 5 cars! The landscaped side yard and a super practical storage shed also add value. In addition, this park has amazingly affordable space rent. You must see this home to fully appreciate it!

Charming turn-key home privately nestled amongst nature that offers year round living. This sale includes a second lot that offers privacy or the potential to expand. Cozy layout featuring 2-beds and 1 bath, large windows throughout, and a wood stove in the heart of the home. Hardwood floors throughout, vaulted ceilings in the main with beautiful wood paneling. Attached is a one-car garage with work benches. Don't miss out on this peaceful property located in the heart of Point Roberts.

Experience country living just outside the city in this immaculate rambler, situated on shy of an acre lot. This cozy 3-bedroom home showcases pride of ownership & features a wood-burning fireplace, numerous updates over the past five years including new appliances, paint, trim, flooring, and more! Step outside to enjoy the peaceful outdoor space with fruit trees, berry bushes, a garden area, a shop, & a lawn mower shed. The level yard offers ample room for expansion & includes covered RV parking, providing space for all your toys. Conveniently located off the Guide Meridian, with Bellingham to the south & Lynden to the north, this home is close to many amenities. Dont miss this opportunity to embrace nature & privacy

Northwest's excellent, level, creek-front building site. Lot #1 in the Glenhaven neighborhood. Glenhaven public water is available; a fire hydrant is right next to the lot. Wave Broadband Cable has high-speed internet service, and electricity is available in the street. Community features include a walking/hiking trail, two boat launches, two lakes, a clubhouse, a HUGE new inground public pool, tennis courts, a playground with swings, a sandbox, and more. Lots of great fishing in the two lakes. The community has a fishing derby every year!! This area has the option to access Burlington or Mt Baker Schools. Also, the building site is fully approved. Wetland mitigation and creek setback is approved.

Masterpiece of a property on 2 acres with Baker view. 1919 farmhouse that has the most thoughtful, thorough, professional makeover that you may ever see. Stunning result of hard work and dedication to doing it right. Everything from the subzero fridge/ freezer, new floors, roof, int/ext paint, insulated outbuildings, trex decks, solid wood custom cabinetry, new natural gas furnace along with solar panels that power the entire property for approx $7.00/month, in ground sprinkler system thru-out entire prop., smart thermostat, chefs pantry, 3 car garage, AND the baker view. So much to offer! Large barn, shop and office are meticulously maintained and offer a variety of uses. This is a package that must be seen to be appreciated.

Prime location in the beautifully maintained Highlands II development. Enjoy the ease of main floor living with the primary bedroom located on the main level, complete with a walk-in closet and master bath. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide ample space for guests or a home office. The kitchen is equipped with plenty of cabinet space, and a large island, making it the heart of the home. The open-plan living and dining areas are perfect for both entertaining and everyday living, featuring large windows that allow natural light to flood the space. Proximity to Whatcom Falls Park, Galbraith Trail System, and Samish Crest Open Space provides endless opportunities for outdoor activities.

Nestled in Maple Falls, this rambler features a bright, open layout on a private, fully fenced lot in a new neighborhood. This cozy home has 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and a 3 car garage. Backyard offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality with a large covered patio area, raised garden beds, greenhouse and fruit trees. A home generator is installed that can power the entire house without hassle. Located 30 minutes from Bellingham and Lynden and 50 minutes from Mount Baker Ski Area. Come see what this home has to offer!

Nestled on a 365 day lot (rare!), reside in the picturesque seaside community in Birch Bay, just a short walk to the beach. Enjoy activities like clamming & sunbathing on a mile-long stretch of beach. This fully updated 2 bed, 1.75 Bath including a steam shower, situated in the secure Latitude 49 Community, renowned for its excellent association amenities. Features include a refreshing outdoor pool & spa, a mini-golf course, laundry facilities, & spacious clubhouse. Just minutes from the Canadian border. An additional lot (#112 - 180 day lot) is included for RV parking, both lots fully fenced, w/ 2 detached outbuildings w/ windows & skylights, providing a great work space or storage. Beautiful paved patio perfect for entertaining!

This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath rambler is on a sunny lot at the end of a cul-de-sac. The light and bright central kitchen looks out in to the beautiful fenced backyard. Large deck and patio area for entertaining. Flex space off of the central kitchen can be used as an office, den or bedroom. Low maintenance yard with garden. Great walkability! Close to the Railroad Trail to Barkley Village, Roosevelt School and Whatcom Falls Park. RV parking.

True waterfront living and the best the Pacific Northwest has to offer! 75' of no-bank direct waterfront access in Birch Bay Village on iconic lower Nakat Way. Easy living with walking distance to all amenities: golf, pickleball, clubhouse & private marina. The 180 degree view is completely unobstructed & stunning. Breathtaking views from every room capture the majesty of Mt Baker & San Juan Islands, but the simple, gentle access to the beach makes this a truly one-of-a-kind waterfront property. From the private entry courtyard to the backyard patio, everything in this home has been designed to showcase the view. Exceptional & purposefully renovated, this 3, 100 sqft single-story home offers an unparalleled experience of luxury living.

Welcome to your future homea charming, single-level, 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom gem in a highly sought-after neighborhood. This delightful property blends comfort, convenience, and privacy. The large, flat yard is mostly fenced. Inside, you'll find a bright living room with large windows, an open dining area off the kitchen. All appliances are included. The three bedrooms offer peaceful retreats with ample closet space. An attached one-car garage provides secure parking and a little extra storage. Located close to town and schools, this home offers a quiet, private setting with easy access to amenities. Great roof, newer furnace and hot water heater tank too. Just a bit of elbow grease and the home will shine.

Welcome to Hawks Landing! This beautiful, new construction home offers 3 beds, 2 bath, and a bonus space with 2181 sq/ft of living space. The open concept great room is complete with vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, SS appliances and quartz countertops, that opens out to a covered patio and a private backyard. A primary suite is privately located on the separate end of the home with dual vanities, a soaking tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet. Located just 15 minutes from Bellingham, Lynden and Nooksack.

Discover this nicely updated 3br/1.75ba home in the coveted 55+ community of Royal Coachman Estates. A host of recent upgrades and meticulous cleanliness, including a brand new furnace installed in June 2024, this residence is a true gem. Enjoy breathtaking views of Mt. Baker from the expansive deck, complete with ample storage and two additional outbuildings, including a workshop. With recent interior paint, roof and gutter maintenance, and pressure washed decks awaiting a fresh stain when weather permits, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Ideal layout with the primary bedroom at one end and two additional bedrooms at the opposite end ensures privacy and flexibility. Experience affordable living in Lynden, WA.

Exquisite residence w/ 2 pristine usable acres, a detached 1, 026 sf guest-house complete w/ garage, kitchenette, 1 Bed, 1 Bath, living, & laundry. The main home spans 2, 872 sf, complemented by attached 1, 082 sf 3-car garage. Vaulted ceilings enhance the expansive feel while the huge kitchen boasts heated flooring, central island, elegant cabinetry, quartz counters, top-tier appliances. Each bed w/ its own ensuite bath & walk-in closet. Central vac system. The seamless one-story open floor plan is designed for entertaining. The homes location in an architecturally distinguished neighborhood ensures the protection of your investment; while the design, floor plan, finishes, & guest-house uses add to the propertys appeal.

Country living close to town! This MUST SEE 3 bedroom, 1 bath home sits on a spacious fully fenced 1/2 acre lot with gorgeous mature trees, raised fenced garden beds, chicken coop, small barn/shop AND a livestock loafing shed with a paddock for all the farm animals. Many upgrades include; updated kitchen, remodeled bathroom, and new siding! Get cozy in front of the fireplace, or enjoy soaking up the sun in your large private back yard. Easy commute to both Bellingham and Lynden. Lynden school district. Make your hobby farm dreams come true today!

Sterling custom craftsmanship & attention to detail greet you in this stunning contemporary waterfront home (100+ ft). Pride of ownership exudes throughout. Gorgeous views of Mt. Baker, Canadian Coastal range & Hales Passage from every room! The up close & personal experience w/ waterfront living is unmatched; spend countless hours watching nature at its finest. Nearly completely rebuilt in 2007, desirable upgrades have been completed. Primary ensuite offers main floor living. Fir trim & beautiful wood floors throughout, chef's kitchen + wrap-around composite deck. Appx 3, 850 sq ft in total which includes separate living area (with views) ideal for extra guest space, rental or home office/studio, 2 car garage & extra parking for boat or RV.
nearby_schools: Lummi High School, Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School

text: Dont miss this stunning 3 bed, 2.25 bath, 1, 852 sq ft home with huge bonus room located in the desirable Lincoln Green neighborhood! The large 11, 593 sq ft lot with views out over a park-like green space is unique in this neighborhood giving you space to take a deep breath and relax. Meticulously maintained, this home features tons of natural light, custom cherry cabinets & granite countertops throughout, and 2 car garage. The open concept main floor includes a gas fireplace, half bath, two eating options with bar seating or dining area that flows out to a patio in the fully fenced backyard. Theres no end to possibilities for entertaining, gardening, or anything your heart desires, just minutes from Drayton Harbor & Birch Bay waterfront!

Nestled in the serene PNW landscape, this 2-bed, 1-bath haven sprawls across 2 private lots, offering views of the vistas of mountains and sea. Wake up to the majestic calls of eagles and savor your morning coffee amidst the tranquil garden space. This charming rambler, enveloped in nature, hosts unparalleled privacy. Community perks include a boat dock, clubhouse, swimming lake, and beach rights for endless outdoor enjoyment. Rest easy with a fully installed generator. Plus, a bonus shipping container, currently serving as an inspiring art space, provides additional flex space. Your PNW oasis awaits!

text: Great location for this single level home in desirable mid county. Totally remodeled interior in 2016 including exterior hardi-plank siding. NEW features include large kitchen island, stainless appliances, cabinets, laminate wood floor, tiled shower in primary bathroom, double sinks, walk-in closet, new hallway storage cabinets, 5 panel interior doors, hot water tank, fireplace insert, spacious timber-tech deck. Home on 1 acre lot & complete with fully fenced large back yard. A new insulated shop added in 2019 with heated finished rec-room attached. Plenty of garden space, dog kennel, 3 outbuildings, a shed full of firewood and riding lawnmower included!

Escape to tranquility & serenading sounds of the seasonal creek! Find solace on one of the resort-style patios or unwind on the walk-out view deck listening to birds sing. Luxury upgrades grace every floor of this spacious 4 bed/3.5 bath open concept home. Prepare to be spoiled with custom crafted doors, top of the line hardware & stone. Engineered hardwood & gorgeous reclaimed solid white oak beams bring warmth and beauty. Jenn-Air appliances, radiant heat & double tankless hot water heaters ensure endless comfort. Create your haven in the rec room: movie, game, or home office. Manicured yard leads to your private foot bridge & on to Lake Whatcom's secluded AM/PM beach to swim/kayak. Golf, tennis, pool & marina are just around the corner.

Your warm & inviting mountain retreat awaits in the coveted Snowline Community Club neighborhood! Unrivaled amenities include gated entry, outdoor pool, tennis courts, fishing pond, playground, walking trails, community clubhouse & is located at the base of Mt. Baker Ski Resort = year round fun! Currently a vacation rental, the opportunity exists to continue using the home as an income earning property or for this PNW charmer to be your full time residence. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, gas range & beautiful cedar cabinetry. Relax & unwind in your private hot tub or take a leisurely stroll, it's just a short walk to the Nooksack River trail. Recent $60K in updates - new heat pump, hot tub, generator & hot water tank.

Dialed in! Bright and Inviting Home Nestled on 2 large lots totaling over 1/3 of an acre! Master Carpenter tirelessly worked on this home over the past few years! Project was Fully Permitted, taken down to the studs and completely rebuilt. New Everything! (Sheeting, Roof, Plumbing, Electric, Furnace, Flooring, Doors, Trim, Cabinets, Sheetrock, Windows, 2x6 Framing, EVERYTHING). Open floor plan, striking stone fireplace, plenty of natural light, and a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Flexible lower level space with separate entrance, wired/plumbed for bar or 2nd kitchen, tons of storage. Sudden Valley amenities: golf course, marina, hiking trails, pool, tennis courts, beaches.... Partial Lake view.
